title: December Orden Family FNL
desc: The Ted and Hedy Orden & Family FNL?is the premiere young professional Shabbat experience. FNL Oneg Shabbat Dinner is for ages 21-39 only and requires an eventbrite ticket. Oneg Dinner tickets include drinks, full dinner & dessert - registration is REQUIRED by 4:30 pm on the Friday of FNL . Unregistered guests will not be allowed to join for dinner.
